ED_Title: Maintenance of international security — good-neighbourliness, stability and development in South-Eastern Europe
ED_DecisionText: At its 45th plenary meeting, on 5 December 2018, the General Assembly, on the recommendation of the First Committee , decided to include in the provisional agenda of its seventy-fifth session the item entitled “Maintenance of international security — good-neighbourliness, stability and development in South-Eastern Europe”.
